{
  "description": "A wide shot depicts a busy port scene with several large, white container cranes dominating the foreground. These cranes are positioned along a long pier extending into calm, dark blue water. A large container ship, carrying red and black shipping containers, is docked alongside the pier, being loaded or unloaded by one of the cranes. The cranes have prominent 'Port of Oakland' branding on their sides. In the background, a hilly coastline with trees and buildings can be seen under a bright blue sky with scattered white clouds. A smaller, yellow crane is also visible on the far right. The overall scene conveys a sense of industrial activity and maritime commerce.",
